><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=251429" target="_blank">Elven Berserk of 53 Dances</a></b><br><em>"The Power of Metal flowing in your veins... at the Speed of Light!"</em><br></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukirle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kirle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 258<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/30/02 6:10:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4049.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need opinions on haste item</span><hr size=1> HASTE&gt;Stat in your case, you could spend a long time in seb and never see a RBG or SBC drop, And to answer your other question wear it all the time, Haste will improve your DPS, making you kill things quicker and in turn allowing you to gain exp quicker. <p>Kirle Koward55 Ale-Slinging Warrior</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uaarlonbladefury.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aarlon Bladefury</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 56<br> <font color=#FF0000>(9/30/02 6:51:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4049.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Need opinions on haste item</span><hr size=1> Use the haste all the time.  If you are the main tank then you use the haste for aggro.  If you aren't MT, why do you care if you lose AC anyway and the DPS is better. <p><p align="center"><img src="http://www.circleofpride.com/members/lavondyss/Aarlon2.jpg" width="238"height="300"></p><BR><p align="center">